## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification

1. Start the app (`/start` workflow), log in as a regular user
2. Open a notebook → chat → send a question and get an AI response
3. Verify 3 new buttons (like, dislike, report) appear below the AI answer, to the right of the existing Save/Copy buttons
4. Click Like → toast confirms success
5. Click Dislike → toast confirms success
6. Click Report → dialog opens → enter report text → submit → toast confirms
7. Log in as admin → navigate to Admin > Feedback page
8. Verify the table shows the feedback entries with correct data
9. Test filters: select "Like" type → only likes shown; set date range → results filtered
